text:
Select a theme for the map that you made. 
(It will be applied to your profile card.)

Your photo was saved and applied to your 
profile card. (You can only save 1 image.)

View the profile cards you have 
obtained at the Tower of Trials.

Erase all stamps? 
(This cannot be undone.)

Due to a change in language setting, 
your comment has been reset.

Edit your profile card's text and 
customize its appearance.

You have exceeded the number of profile cards 
allowed. Please delete enough profile cards to 
fit within the limit.
Save Relay Trial players' profile cards?

The Community Guidelines apply to shared 
content and can be found on Nintendo's website. 
Please be considerate to your fellow players.

Snap a photo of your favorite 
allies for your profile card.

Choose a privacy setting for your profile card. 
(You can change this setting at any time. 
Note: changes will not affect cards that have 
already been exchanged.)

You can change the privacy setting 
for your profile card.

This setting is restricted by parental controls 
and cannot be changed.

Choose a display setting for profile card stamps. 
(You can change this setting at any time.)

You can choose whether to show 
or hide stamps on the profile cards 
you have obtained.
"If this is war, so be it!"
